snippet.textDisplay:
It's only Sajid Ali on flute and Aahad Nayani on drums who shine in this really weak composition. Sara Haider is under-utilised or rather wasted. 
Also, Season 9 is being labeled as being 'too loud' and this song too fits the frame of being loud because of over-the-top production. 
And needless to say, Shani Arshad has come out to be weakest among the lot.
Hope that other songs from the episode make it to the level of CS.
Lots of love!!
